s of food restriction on bat immune response.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Ot\u00e1lora-Ardila, A\u00edda", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Herrera M., L. Gerardo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Flores-Mart\u00ednez, Jos\u00e9 Juan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Welch, Kenneth C.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/985afeed39a616011f82241cb5cc750c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/ecb5f3b93530a94609ec570a7b4abe8938b35897a7629d327e86bf3b4e374c50", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/4NT6ACEU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/4NT6ACEU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/02af2c166d5e4368afe66f1b334c758d!/b226687-229177", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "41-47", "title": "Mammalian Biology", "volume": "82"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/985afeed39a616011f82241cb5cc750c"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:4NT6ACEU"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/J.MAMBIO.2016.11.002"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13527919"}}]}}, "title": "The effect of shor